title: "Don't default; own your potential"
description: "Maria Cobos, a high school student, often wonders about the meaning of life. She believes that the best way to succeed, to emerge, to become the better version of ourselves, is to be conscious of the decisions we make, and why we make them. Through her talk, she will explore the best ways individuals can live up to their potential and overcome the obstacles that might block the way."
author: María Cobos
